Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:28.31,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Verila som len sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:27.56,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)\fs67.5\bord0\shad0\fnTimes New Roman\pos(675,537.75)\c&HB07260&}Po čele domu stekali kvapky dažďa.
